<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạlmsnạ ạlận</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ṭạlbynk yạ sydnạ tsẖfy mrḍ ạlạ̉jsạd

[V2]
 hnsẖwf ậyạt wʿjạyb wtḥqq ạlạ̉mjạd

[V3]
 ạlqrạr - ạlmsnạ ạlận .. mạlynạ ạ̹ymạn

[V4]
 wạ̹ḥnạ bnʿln ạ̉nk tqdr ṣạḥb ạlslṭạn

[V5]
 2- yạ sẖạfy ạ̉mrạḍ sẖʿbk bdạlẗ ạlbnyn

[V6]
 bnṣly tmd ydk wtftḥ ạlʿynyn

[V7]
 3- ʿdt snyn wbtsẖfy ạ̉mrạḍ bqạlhạ zmạn

[V8]
 wtftḥ ạlạ̉rḥạm tsẖfy mrḍ ạlsrṭạn

[V9]
 4- jạy htʿln ʿn mjdk wạlsẖfạ fy jnạḥyk

[V10]
 nhr ạlsẖfạ ygẖmrnạ hw ysẖạwr ʿlyk

[V11]
 5- jạyyn ṭạlbyn msẖyỷtk wḥty̱ ạ̹n fyh ạ̉sẖwạk

[V12]
 dy nʿmtk tkfynạ wbḥb nmsẖy wrạk</lyrics>
